    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クロエ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chloe</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>コハク</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kohaku</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>27</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>カイウス！！
またこんな辛い物ばっかり作って！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Caius!! Again with you making spicy food!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>しょうがないだろ。
辛い方が好きなんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I can't help it. I really like spicy food.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あたしはもっと
美容にいいものとか食べたいの！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I wanna eat more stuff that's good for beauty!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>スタイルがよくなるように
健康にも気をつけたいの！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I want to improve my figure,
so I have to look after my health!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まあまあ。　少し落ち着かないか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Now, now. Aren't you worrying too much?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そうだよ。
好きな物食べたいっていうのは
自然な事だししょうがないよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>She's right. It's only natural to eat the
things you like, so it's not a big deal.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>27</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なによ、あなた達！
自分達はちょっとスタイルいいからって！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>What the heck is with you people?!
Just 'cause your figures are a bit better
than mine, you don't have to say stuff like that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>嫌味！？　嫌味のつもりなの！？
絶対に許さない！！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Was it sarcasm?! Were you being sarcastic?!
I will absolutely NEVER forgive you!!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>勝負よ！！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Fight me!!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
